description:
"THE IRON SAINT" an Imperial Knight story written by the talented SaggioMik

Narrated and produced by A Vox in the Void

During the Siege of Dharrovar, A Freeblade Knight lays wounded at the bottom of a chasm. With its retinue of Vostroyan Firstborn and Sisters of Battle, it will have to face the onslaught of the heretic forces that approach.
